A vintage 1950s noir-style illustration of a detective with a magnifying glass peering into an elaborate mechanical puzzle box, rendered in muted sepia tones and deep shadows. The puzzle box is partially open, revealing intricate clockwork gears, nested compartments, and hidden drawers within drawers. Mysterious fog swirls around the scene. The detective wears a fedora and trench coat, hunched over a cluttered desk covered with scattered blueprints and technical diagrams. Dramatic lighting from a single desk lamp casts long shadows across weathered wooden surfaces. The mood is investigative and mysterious, suggesting secrets waiting to be uncovered within complex nested structures.
